snippet.title: Liftoff - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the official Launch trailer for Liftoff: an FPV drone racing simulator. 

Liftoff will be released on September 13, 2018 and will be available on Steam for PC, Mac and Linux.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/410340/Liftoff/
